  <Key>UNEXPECTEDDEMISE</Key>
  <Name>Unexpected Demise</Name>
  <Description>Once per session, as an action, the character may spend 2 Destiny Points and make a [B]Hard ([DI][DI][DI]) Perception check[b]. If successful, for the next two rounds the character may spend one maneuver to add on automatic [TR] to his next combat check made in that turn. In addition, for the next two rounds, when the character inflicts a Critical Injury on a rival NPC, the target is immediately incapacitated in the same way as a minion NPC would be (see page 400 of the [B]Force and Destiny[b] Core Rulebook).</Description>
